      <title>印度反对派领导人否认出口民调预测莫迪获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/indian-opposition-leaders-reject-exit-polls-predicting-modi-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度反对派领导人对预测总理纳伦德拉·莫迪将获得压倒性胜利的出口民调结果不以为然，一位高层政治家称其为“莫迪媒体民调”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/indian-opposition-leaders-reject-exit-polls-predicting-modi-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 06:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非选举后争执不休 投资者进退维谷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-coalition-talks-leave-investors-in-limbo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周南非大选未能产生绝对胜利者，而正在进行的联盟谈判的结果仍存在很大的不确定性，投资者准备迎接南非金融市场的进一步动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-coalition-talks-leave-investors-in-limbo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度出口民调显示莫迪获胜，基础设施和国有企业成为最大赢家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/infra-state-firms-big-winners-as-india-exit-polls-show-modi-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于出口民意调查预测总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的执政党将获得压倒性胜利，印度国有企业和基础设施相关公司的股价表现突出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/infra-state-firms-big-winners-as-india-exit-polls-show-modi-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 05:13:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国暂停10个月后再次上调海外投资限额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/china-raises-limit-on-overseas-investment-after-10-month-pause</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国自七月以来首次取消了对海外证券投资的限制，此举可能有助于满足部分日益增长的海外资产需求，尽管北京方面正寻求提振国内市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/china-raises-limit-on-overseas-investment-after-10-month-pause</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 05:05:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼将遣返泰国被控谋杀、贩毒罪的逃犯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-03/indonesia-is-to-deport-a-fugitive-to-thailand-who-is-wanted-on-murder-and-drug-trafficking-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼雅加达（美联社）——官员周一表示，泰国头号通缉犯之一的逃犯将在印尼旅游岛巴厘岛被捕，随后乘坐泰国空军飞机回国。此前，他因在祖国犯下多起杀人罪和贩毒罪而在逃数月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-03/indonesia-is-to-deport-a-fugitive-to-thailand-who-is-wanted-on-murder-and-drug-trafficking-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 04:56:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谢因鲍姆有望成为墨西哥首位女总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/sheinbaum-to-win-mexico-vote-by-large-margin-exit-polls-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克劳迪娅·希恩鲍姆有望以压倒性优势成为墨西哥首位女性领导人，她将利用即将卸任的总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔的支持率，但同时也继承了其政府留下的猖獗的犯罪暴力和巨大的财政赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/sheinbaum-to-win-mexico-vote-by-large-margin-exit-polls-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:04:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称在中央政府工作的夫妇为英国进行间谍活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/china-says-couple-who-worked-in-central-government-spied-for-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国称，一对在中央政府任职的夫妇被发现为英国从事间谍活动，这进一步加剧了两国之间因间谍指控而产生的争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/china-says-couple-who-worked-in-central-government-spied-for-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克鲁格曼称中国“奇怪地不愿”刺激需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/krugman-says-china-is-bizarrely-unwilling-to-boost-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺贝尔经济学奖得主保罗·克鲁格曼表示，中国领导人“奇怪地不愿意”利用更多的政府支出来支持消费需求而不是生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/krugman-says-china-is-bizarrely-unwilling-to-boost-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:51:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基与马科斯在峰会上抨击中国 加强关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/zelenskiy-to-visit-philippines-after-singapore-forum-rappler</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基周一在马尼拉会见了菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯。此前一天，两国领导人在安全峰会上发表了对中国的严厉批评声明。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/zelenskiy-to-visit-philippines-after-singapore-forum-rappler</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 23:24:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本石川地区发生 5.9 级地震</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-02/strong-earthquakes-shake-area-near-japanese-region-hit-by-jan-1-fatal-disaster-but-no-tsunami</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京（美联社）——周一凌晨地震再次袭击日本中北部地区石川，该地区仍未从 1 月 1 日强烈地震造成的破坏中恢复，但最新的震动并未造成重大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-02/strong-earthquakes-shake-area-near-japanese-region-hit-by-jan-1-fatal-disaster-but-no-tsunami</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 22:04:47 GMT</pubDate>
